Marta May https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marta_May 0 Marta May, born María Jesús Mayor Ávila (14 June 1939) is a Spanish actress. In 1968 she was awarded by the Círculo de Escritores Cinematográficos for best actress in La piel quemada.In 1975 Esteban Durán directed Algo de ti en el arcoiris at the Teatro Don Juan in Barcelona, and it starred Alejandro Ulloa, Marta May, and Eduardo Criado.
